channel.description:
Welcome to ODN - On Demand News.

Formerly the ITN YouTube channel, ODN is your home for the top visual stories happening across the globe. You can depend on ODN for the latest news footage and reports from conflict zones and current affairs events around the world. But we also understand that your feed needs the occasional uplifting or quirky story as well, so we have a bit of that for you too.

On Demand News takes a different approach to your typical broadcast news providers, catering exclusively for our digital audience.
